N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 189.5 - Transportation or shipment of carcasses and parts through new york

State Regulations
A person may transport or ship carcasses or parts of any
CWD susceptible animals through New York provided that all such carcasses and
parts are not disposed of in any manner or delivered to any person in New
